          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Sunshine Protection Act of 2018</b></p> <p>The bill amends the Uniform Time Act of 1966 to make daylight savings time the new, permanent standard time.</p> <p>States with areas exempt from daylight savings time may choose the standard time for those areas.</p>]]></text>
